# src/styles/ Directory Rules

## Do Not Manually Edit These Files

- **intuit.css** — Synced from the DDMS CDN via `npm run sync-tokens`. Contains all IDS design token CSS custom properties. Run `npm run sync-tokens [version]` to update.
- **index.css** — Global styles. Should not need modification during prototyping.
- **fonts.css** — Font imports. Should not need modification during prototyping.

## Editable Files

- **App.module.css** — All prototype-specific styling goes here. Uses CSS Modules (Vite auto-scopes `.module.css` files) and design tokens.

## References

- **Design Tokens**: `.cursor/rules/tokens/intuit/*.mdc`
- **Token Overview**: `.cursor/rules/tokens.mdc`
- **Component Rules**: `.cursor/rules/components/*.mdc`
- **Design System**: `.cursor/rules/design-system.mdc`
